#Command Briefing

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("Red Alert! The SD Malphas has launched a direct assault on the Erebus. They aren't using bombers—they're using high-speed boarding pods.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("These 'Breach Pods' are filled with Shivan ground troops and biological spores. If they penetrate the hull, we lose the ship from the inside out.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none

$Stage Text:
 XSTR("All available fighters are to be scrambled immediately. You are the last line of defense. If the Erebus falls, we are all dead.", -1)
$end_multi_text
$Ani Filename: <default>
+Wave Filename: none


